      "writtenOn": "2018-06-07T17:47:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The doc is incomplete. If the underlying call returns something other than appengine.MultiError, it is returned as is (can be traced from here https://github.com/luci/gae/blob/master/impl/prod/raw_datastore.go#L143). The underlying call returns MultiError only if RPC succeeds. Otherwise it returns an RCP error: https://github.com/golang/appengine/blob/master/datastore/datastore.go#L275\n\nAlso I believe I saw deadline RPC errors for real myself.",
